{"tid":6834,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"印青年機油塗黑全身扮鬼 欲強姦女鄰居","createTime":"2016-11-27T14:34:58.000Z","updateTime":"2016-11-28T20:08:32.000Z","uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f7aac03fdec0e56985878f523bd1f9f28bb5e64d","tid":6834,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T14:34:58.000Z","msg":"馬來西亞一名印度裔青年，涉嫌用汽車機油把全身塗黑，扮成所謂「油鬼仔」，深夜摸黑由屋頂潛入鄰居家中，企圖強姦女戶主，但事敗落荒而逃。 <br />\n<br />\n案發時，男女戶主已入睡，但一對年幼子女還沒睡覺，他們聽到屋頂傳來走路聲，於是慌忙叫醒父母。男戶主到廚房查看，只遠遠見到對方僅穿一條內褲，全身塗黑。他喚醒鄰居協助搜捕，但仍被「油鬼仔」逃去。 <br />\n不過，男戶主在屋頂找到疑犯的衣物、手機和銀包，裏面有疑犯的身份證，證實屬居於附近一名21歲印度裔青年。 <br />\n警方相信疑犯是垂涎31歲女戶主的美色，欲深夜潛入施暴，唯未得手便行蹤敗露，正全力搜尋他歸案。"},{"pid":"66021773216bd37acbe81c483f0dfe919a0cf2b7","tid":6834,"uid":30807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T14:37:33.000Z","msg":"又會離遠都見到係油黑<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ddd4a8a376a4c7b4207d1eb9eba78644c4ca0842","tid":6834,"uid":6213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T14:38:09.000Z","msg":"好醒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a5b61a379b68cbabdf2db299cd863c1decefee4","tid":6834,"uid":1374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T14:39:51.000Z","msg":"印度人仲要塗黑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ?"},{"pid":"0d193740f9140b66d87159e43d98b6b0906f0baa","tid":6834,"uid":30807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T14:42:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>印度人仲要塗黑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n朱古力同炭都係有差距"},{"pid":"53b27f3be9bfa708eacab1e95cb335931ad0d3ca","tid":6834,"uid":2949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T14:43:40.000Z","msg":"俾鬼屌就唔會反抗？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23d25ad76d9fd87d03711048371212efddf2ed9b","tid":6834,"uid":29273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":